verbose_text: Moreover, U2OS / MTX300 cells stably expressing both CK1gamma2 and IRS4-S859A had higher p-Akt levels and tumor weights, and larger tumor sizes than those stably expressing both CK1gamma2 and IRS4-WT when they were subcutaneously inoculated into nude mice, although the growth of U2OS / MTX300 cells stably expressing IRS4-WT were similar to those stably expressing IRS4-S859A in nude mice.
